    <body>
        <header class="main-header">
            <nav class="main-header__nav">
                <ul class="main-header__item-list">
                    <li class="main-header__item"><a href="/">Home Page</a></li>
                    <li class="main-header__item"><a href="/tour_options">Tour Options</a></li>
                </ul>  
            </nav>
        </header>
        <div class="firstSection"> 
            <h1>Welcome to Fernando de Noronha!</h1>
            <p class="sOne"> This is one of the most beautiful islands in the world </p>
            <p class="sOne"> Located 350 kilometers (218 miles) off the northeastern coast of Brazil.</p>
            <p class="sOne"> Fernando de Noronha is a volcanic archipelago made up of 21 islands and is a protected marine national park.</p>
            <p class="sOne">There are plenty of activities to do, if you stay here for a week you will get to know everything about the island.</p>
            <br>
            <p class="sOneSpecial">Please, type one activity you would like to do here</p>
            <form action="/beaches/noronha" method="POST">
                <label>What would you like to do first?</label><br>
                <input name="noronhaActivity" type="text" placeholder="hiking or diving">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">GO!</button>
            </form>
            <form action="/end_tour">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning">End tour</button>
            </form>
        </div> 
